<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="put-through">put through</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>使经受 (困难或令人不悦的事情)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I told myself I would not put my mom through that pain again. 
我告诉自己不能再让妈妈经受那样的痛苦了。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>安排某人上学；供某人上学：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She worked as a waitress to put herself through college. 
她当服务员挣钱来供自己上大学。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>为...接通电话；接通 (电话)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Could you put me through to the manager, please?
请帮我接通经理的电话，好吗？</p></div></div>